Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Neighborhood theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/neighborhood.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Neighborhood is super responsive, retina ready, and built upon the 1170px Twitter Bootstrap framework. Featuring a clean, modern, and superbly slick design, packed with the most powerful Swift Framework which offers limitless possibilities.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341\" target=\"_blank\">Download Neighborhood theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Quins theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/quins-bs-creative-wordpress-themes/7037698\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/quins.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Creative WordPress portfolio/agency Theme with clean and modern design.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/quins-bs-creative-wordpress-themes/7037698\">Purchase Quins theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">WP Ultimate Recipe plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.wpultimaterecipe.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/recipe.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A beautiful and user-friendly recipe plugin for WordPress.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.wpultimaterecipe.com/\">Download WP Ultimate Recipe plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Slash Admin plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/slash-admin/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/slash.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Slash Admin gathers some common functions and lets you change various different options in a WordPress website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/slash-admin/\">Download Slash Admin plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i