gins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Storefront theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.woothemes.com/storefront/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/storefront.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A free WordPress theme offering deep integration with WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.woothemes.com/storefront/\" target=\"_blank\">Download Storefront theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">T-ONE theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/tone-clean-minimal-wordpress-theme/7602385\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/tone.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Creative &#038; responsive WordPress Theme featuring clean and minimal design suitable for any studio, agencies, portfolio, graphic designers, etc.. Powered with Twitter Bootstrap &#038; Redux Framework. It can be customized easily to suit your wishes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/tone-clean-minimal-wordpress-theme/7602385\">Purchase T-ONE theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Cardinal Theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cardinal-wordpress-theme/8070889\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cardinal.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Cardinal is mobile ready, creative multi-purpose theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cardinal-wordpress-theme/8070889\">Purchase Cardinal theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Javo Directory Theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/javo-directory-wordpress-theme/8390513\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/javo.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Maya is a composable and clean wordpress template. You can create amazing homes and impressive internal pages.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/javo-directory-wordpress-theme/8390513\">Purchase Javo Directory theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Search and Filter Pro Plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.designsandcode.com/wordpress-plugins/search-filter-pro/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/search-filter1.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Search by custom fields, post meta, taxonomies, tags, categories, authors, post types, post dates and more – The Ultimate WordPress Filter Plugin with Ajax!</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.designsandcode.com/wordpress-plugins/search-filter-pro/\">Purchase Search and Filter Plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=tqC-96Gxu08:0SEpSbl1I6E:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=tqC-96Gxu08:0SEpSbl1I6E:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=tqC-96Gxu08:0SEpSbl1I6E:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=tqC-96Gxu08:0SEpSbl1I6E:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0